@police_affairs
title: Police affairs 
subtitle: We can set our police policy. 
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0 and spd_in_government and interior_minister == "Sollmann"
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?][? if not spd_in_government : The <span style="color: #c00000;">SPD</span> is not in government. ?][? if interior_minister != "Sollmann": Sollmann is not the Interior minister. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; police_timer -= 6; last_advisor_action = 1
go-to: police

@cologne_campaign
title: Campaign in the Rhineland
subtitle: Sollmann is the editor of a newspaper in Cologne. He can sway some local support to our party.
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: catholics_spd += 2*(1-dissent); new_middle_spd += 1*(1-dissent); workers_spd += 1*(1-dissent)

Some readers may have made up there mind about us.
